These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, japanese, turkish, colombian
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, cherry, peach
1. the person eating peach is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the colombian is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | colombian | turkish |
| Food        | grapefruit | kiwi   | peach | cherry    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, fanta, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, social-worker, fisherman, software-developer
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the musician is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
4. the musician is the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the musician is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | soy-milk  | 7up  | coffee |
| Job   | software-developer    | musician | fisherman | social-worker    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, weightlifting, climbing, volleyball
4 different games are played: chess, whist, snooker, domino
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
2. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | volleyball | climbing | weightlifting    | soccer      |
| Game   | snooker        | domino     | chess | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
House: wooden, cottage, victorian, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, american, nigerian, japanese
1. the cottage house is between the russian and the japanese##2
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the wooden house##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the american is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the american is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House         | futuristic | wooden | cottage | victorian |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | russian   | american    | japanese  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, hedgehog, frog
There 4 different types of food: papaya, artichoke, kale, lemon
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person eating artichoke is the owner of the frog##1
3. the person eating kale is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | snake  | lizard    | hedgehog   | frog       |
| Food   | papaya | lemon | kale | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, plum, orange, cherry
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, aquamarine, light-blue, azure
1. the person who likes aquamarine is in an even position##4
2. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person eating orange is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food   | orange      | plum | cherry | kiwi |
| Color   | azure | aquamarine     | yellow  | light-blue  |

