.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, rose, aconite, begonia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, metal, ambient, dubstep
1. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the fan of dubstep is the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
6. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower   | poppy | begonia | aconite | rose    |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep | ambient  | folk     | metal |

