.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
City: edinburgh, miami, hannover, nizza
There 4 different types of food: onion, tomato, apricot, potato
1. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
2. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person eating potato##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to miami##2
6. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating tomato is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person eating apricot##2
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| City   | miami | edinburgh      | nizza | hannover |
| Food   | onion  | potato | tomato    | apricot            |

