.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, photographer, chef, project-manager
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, daisy, azalea, bellflower
1. the chef is on the left or right of the musician##3
2. the musician is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsdaisy and the chef##2
4. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
5. the chef is the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | project-manager | photographer   | musician | chef |
| Flower    | bellflower     | daisy | rose     | azalea  |

