.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cabbage, spinach, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, mystery, sports
1. the person eating cranberry is the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person eating spinach##2
4. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
6. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Food      | cabbage       | spinach   | cranberry | zucchini |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | drama | sports        | comedy    |

