.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, amber, mauve, purple
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, amaryllis, azalea
1. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Color   | turquise   | purple   | amber      | mauve      |
| Flower      | begonia | amaryllis | azalea | orchid |

