.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, volleyball, snowboarding
House: cottage, gothic-revival, ranch-style, colonial
1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the gothic-revival house and the ranch-style house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Sport          | snowboarding | swimming  | volleyball  | soccer |
| House   | colonial  | ranch-style | cottage | gothic-revival   |

