3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| City   | edinburgh | miami | paris | new-york  |
| Sport     | cricket   | surfing  | baseball  | ice-hockey |

