.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, badminton, basketball, soccer
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, radish, zucchini, cauliflower
1. the person eating zucchini is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
6. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Sport   | basketball | soccer | surfing | badminton |
| Food           | cauliflower     | cucumber     | zucchini   | radish         |

