.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, snowmobile, train
City: venice, colone, london, miami
1. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the bus##2
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
6. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Transport   | train | bus         | quad-bike   | snowmobile |
| City   | london    | colone | miami | venice   |

