.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, quad-bike, bike
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, social-worker, mechanic, police-officer
1. the police-officer is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the mechanic is the person driving the car##1
3. the social-worker is the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
5. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Transport   | roller | car | quad-bike    | bike |
| Job   | electrician   | mechanic  | police-officer | social-worker     |

