.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, fantasy, musical, drama
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, march, august
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | drama   | musical | horror | fantasy    |
| Birthday   | march | february  | august     | april |

