.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, wooden, farmhouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, musical, satire
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
2. the wooden house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
3. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
7. the person watching animation movies is the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| House   | farmhouse | craftsman    | wooden       | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre       | disaster  | musical | satire | animation  |

