.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, may, august
4 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, rabbit, horse
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | december | may | march  | august |
| Pet     | mouse      | rabbit       | dog | horse     |

