.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, time-travel, romance
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, ebony, mauve, blood-red
1. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
3. the person who likes ebony is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who likes green##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
6. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | time-travel   | romance | comedy |
| Color   | blood-red          | ebony | green         | mauve  |

 